# fleet-deps — ignore list
#
# One repo name OR package name per line. Matched names (and any edges
# touching them) are dropped from the graph. Use '#' for comments.
#
# Useful for unarchived-but-inactive projects that pollute the report.
# Archiving the repo on GitHub is the cleaner option when feasible — the
# graph filter (isArchived == false) already excludes those automatically.

# Patterns may use '*' as a wildcard (e.g. 'grunt-*' matches all grunt-prefixed
# names). Without a wildcard, the match is exact.

dcl
grunt-*

